law.text:
This subtitle does not apply to:
An attorney licensed to practice law in the State;
An individual authorized to represent individuals in immigration matters under 8 C.F.R. § 292.1;
A nonprofit organization that has been recognized under 8 C.F.R. § 292.2;
A representative of a nonprofit organization that has been recognized under 8 C.F.R. § 292.2; or
A clinic affiliated with a law school in the State.
